                <span class="absolute inset-[-1000%] animate-[spin_2s_linear_infinite] bg-[conic-gradient(from_90deg_at_50%_50%,#a855f7_0%,#3b82f6_50%,#a855f7_100%)]"></span>
                <span class="inline-flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-zinc-950 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-purple-300 backdrop-blur-3xl">
                    O que voce pode criar
                </span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="sc-title">Descreva. <span class="sc-grad">A Aron constroi.</span></h2>
            <p class="sc-lead">Sites, aplicativos fullstack, dashboards e jogos — com codigo real, design premium e tudo
                funcionando de verdade. Veja acontecer.</p>
